UPGRADE
=======================

### General
 * Upload a image cover for Movie
 * Update medias content in relation with movies


### BDD
* ALTER TABLE  `movies` ADD  `image` VARCHAR( 250 ) NULL AFTER  `description` ;
* DROP TABLE `medias_movies`
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `facebookId` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL AFTER  `id` ;
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `facebookAccessToken` VARCHAR(255) INT NOT NULL AFTER  `id` ;
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `googleId` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL AFTER  `id` ;
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `googleAccessToken` VARCHAR(255) INT NOT NULL AFTER  `id` ;
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `twitterAccessToken` VARCHAR( 255 ) NULL AFTER  `facebookAccessToken` ;
* ALTER TABLE  `user` ADD  `twitterId` VARCHAR( 255 ) NULL AFTER  `facebookAccessToken` ;

